				<td colspan="2"><span>Makes sense Mose -- same reason why dots on different mobs pulse at different times.  I think everyone has 6-second server ticks, but they aren't at all related to anyone else's.  Has something to do with spawntime (or when you zoned in).
<br />

<br />
For instance -- if you ever AE 2+ mobs that are triggered (spawn together) then your dots pulse together.  Pull two that spawned at different times, and the dots pulse differently.
<br />

<br />
Its rather interesting, and helps explain the duration.
<br />

<br />
I suspect it was a combo of people not trusting you and thus waiting back, sticking on each other in midair, and the song lasting its very minimum (min 3-ticks is what, 13 seconds?)
<br />

<br />
Tril</span></td>
